# 3D Models Directory

Place GLTF/GLB models in the appropriate subdirectory:

- furniture/    - Tables, chairs, bar stools, booths
- equipment/    - Coffee machines, refrigerators, displays
- decoration/   - Plants, lamps, wall art
- custom/       - User-uploaded custom models

## Recommended Model Sources (Free)

- Sketchfab: https://sketchfab.com/3d-models?features=downloadable
- Poly Pizza: https://poly.pizza/
- Kenney Assets: https://kenney.nl/assets

## Model Requirements

- Format: GLTF or GLB
- Optimized for web (< 5MB per model recommended)
- Draco compression supported
- Animations supported (named clips)
